<title>USA: Continental Investment names president.</title>
<headline>Continental Investment names president.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1997-07-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Continental Investment Corp said Monday that Chairman and Chief Executive R. Dale Sterritt has been appointed to the additional posts of president and treasurer.</p>
<p>He succeeds Thomas Snodgrass, who died recently.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
